metadata.description:
Dear Chris,

I accidentally sent 10 ETH to your address while trying to bid against you in the chris.eth auction. Can you please find it in your heart to return them to me? I would sincerely appreciate it more than I can express. I invite you to please keep 3.57 ETH for your troubles to cover the cost of buying chris.eth.

Either this address (0x8cd8C11CCAD3e7ec98338B748a00908683F6EA71) or 0xbf89E0cc29bf4e5595Ae3cbEadA4dDA690D72f31 would work fine. Please do not send them back to the address they came from - that was a coinbase wallet, which I do not control.

Thank you so very kindly.
metadata.name: DEAR CHRIS - PLEASE HELP
